  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>For breakfast you'll have a buffet breakfast each morning with hot and cold options. Guests on half board will have a four-course dinner with choices. You'll have waiter service for the first and main course plus a buffet of starters, salads and desserts which you can help yourself to. </p>
<p>A pool bar is open during the day for light lunches, snacks and refreshing drinks (payable locally).</p>]]></cateringDescription>
