  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Garda Bellevue's near the historic centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/604dbba59ac64320ab6e9f1e89231a4c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/604dbba59ac64320ab6e9f1e89231a4c}" title="Limone">Limone</a> and close to the ferry port, which makes it a great base if you’re planning to spend your time exploring the lake. The hotel's surrounded by lemon groves and olive trees and if you want those picture perfect lake views, just head to the pool area. There are plenty of loungers and a pool bar so you can grab some drinks and snacks. There’s also an indoor pool, which you can find in the spa along with a sauna, steam room and Turkish bath.</p>
<p>End the day with a night cap at the bar and catch up on the day's activities. The bar is also a great place for hanging out and planning your next Lake Garda adventure!</p>
<p>Transfer time: approx. 2 hours 15 mins by coach from Verona airport.</p>]]></description>
