  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Garda Bellevue is a fantastic base for exploring <a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda">Lake Garda</a>. It's in the centre of Limone with the ferry port close by, which makes town-hopping easy! With two swimming pools and a relaxing spa, this is the best place to come back to at the end of the day for some R&amp;R.</p>]]></listingDescription>
